name: CERDNIVERSE 💫
description:
The journey towards success is more like a traveler lost in a desert, desperate to find an oasis, desperate to quench his thirst.
But it is not about how grave the thirst is but about how long he chooses to walk thirsty.

Inspired by Chirag Tulsiani's quote.
This Artwork connected with Amoeba Territory.

Artwork Created by Raganxq
